{"tid":2314363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"揭密中國「墮落天堂」，青年集體淫樂等死","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T17:36:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f4fd0045aac3c90eee7709e75994d2ff8c87e2","tid":2314363,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:18:41.000Z","msg":"現代年輕人起薪不高，生活大不易，不僅職業倦怠，甚至對世界感到厭世；中國就有一群人放棄生計、身份、尊嚴，在繁華的城市角落打造出一處「墮落天堂」。距離深圳市中心不到10公里的龍華新區，有個名叫三和人才市場的地方，一群被稱作「三和大神」的青年長期在該處遊蕩，<strong>他們崇尚「及時行樂」，只要打工賺到幾百元，就立刻把錢花在網咖、買春，貫徹「做1玩3」的守則</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n《網易新聞》報導，「三和大神」秉持打零工、日結精神，只要賺到百來元後，便開始實踐「吃喝嫖賭抽」5字真訣；。。。<br />\n<br />\n吃飽喝足後，三和大神們有些會到網咖，每小時1.5元（約新台幣6元），花上8元（約新台幣34元）就能玩通宵，累了便直接在座位上睡覺；<strong>也有些人則會到市場附近的龍華公園裡「發洩」，報導指出，該處暗藏著大批應召女子，只要30至50元（約新台幣130元至215元）就可以潦草地解決性需求。</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=859878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D859878&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2mINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=55b68cc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D859878&h=56eabfd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=859878</a>"},{"pid":"c6fe3be7094be0a9ca36ae66986aff1ef51ba95a","tid":2314363,"uid":374134,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"Wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4bc9fd3ac2d2d0a4b912b9c2eea2b6e287a1fc","tid":2314363,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭如徹底失敗，可能都變成咁。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed5ca9f00f759c9a603e1477c74b3305d4b88cc","tid":2314363,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fe3be7094be0a9ca36ae66986aff1ef51ba95a","tid":2314363,"uid":374134,"like":2,"dislike":2,"sco